1	//! Shared callback wrapper for event handler closures.
2	//!
3	//! [`Callback`] wraps closures in [`Arc`](alloc::sync::Arc) so they can be
4	//! stored in Props structs, cloned cheaply, and
5	//! compared by pointer identity. `Clone`, `PartialEq`, `Deref`, and `AsRef`
6	//! all delegate to `Arc` with no cfg-gated code.
7	//!
8	//! ## Thread-safety
